If you can't wait until 2025 to see a new iteration of Superman you're in luck! My Adventures with Superman has just finished its freshmen outing but how does it hold up? Does the anime influence help or hurt the very familiar story of our Man of Steel? Where does it fit in the lexicon of Superman media? Check out this episode to find out! If you can, please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

